summary:
Hey @taylorswift! 
I just want to say a massive thank you for showing me so much love in the previous era! 
My all-caps...
body:
Hey @taylorswift!

I just want to say a massive thank you for showing me so much love in the previous era!

My all-caps screaming posts probably gave away how much I love you, but I’ll say it again. I love you so much and I’m so so so grateful for all the love you’ve shown me.

I truly truly truly cannot express how much you liking my posts and putting up with my spamming means to me.

You are such a kind soul and you go above and beyond for all of us.

We really aren’t just your fans but your friends and that means so so so much to me.

I love you with all of my sparkly soul and I will stand by you forever.

THANK YOU for everything.
